# Whitelist approach: only code/ and root docs are tracked for now.
# data/, outputs/, literature/, notes/, galamsey_motivation_files/, rsconnect/,
# and other root files are intentionally excluded (data lives on Dropbox).
/*
!/code/
!/README.md
!/.gitignore

# R / RStudio cruft (in case it appears under code/)
.Rhistory
.Rproj.user/
*.RData
